content.text: You can test your Data Structures and Algorithms skills with W3Schools' Exercises.
content.html: You can test your Data Structures and Algorithms skills with W3Schools' Exercises.

content.text: We have gathered a variety of DSA exercises (with answers) for each DSA Chapter.
content.html: We have gathered a variety of DSA exercises (with answers) for each DSA Chapter.

content.text: Try to solve an exercise by filling in the blanks, or show the answer to see what you've done wrong.
content.html: Try to solve an exercise by filling in the blanks, or show the answer to see what you've done wrong.

content.text: You will get 1 point for each correct answer. Your score and total score will always be displayed.
content.html: You will get 1 point for each correct answer. Your score and total score will always be displayed.

content.text: If you don't know much about Data Structures and Algorithms, we suggest that you read our DSA Tutorial from scratch.
content.html: If you don't know much about Data Structures and Algorithms, we suggest that you read our DSA Tutorial from scratch.
